headers.subject: [tosdr:2784] Elance [bad] Account removal: mutually exclusive terms

html:
While you can terminate your membership Elance "will retain and use your information as necessary" "on our archived database and records." So IMHO you actually can't remove your account, you only can to stop using it.

https://www.elance.com/p/legal/privacy-policy.html
pp.Terminating Your Membership, Data Retention
